# This README is under development:

Basic usage (Rack):

#/config.ru
require 'httpbl'
use Httpbl, :api_key => "#{Your HTTP:BL API key from http://projecthoneypot.org}"

Basic usage (Rails):

#/environment.rb
require 'httpbl'
config.middleware.insert_before Rack::Lock, Httpbl, :api_key => "#{Your HTTP:BL API key from http://projecthoneypot.org}"

